[2026-07-01T09:15:52.508Z] [INFO] [stdout] Socratic Tutor Mode with Guided Questioning Logic has been implemented. Here's what was done:
[2026-07-01T09:15:52.508Z] [INFO] [stdout]   - "What do you think this word means?" (vocabulary/define)
[2026-07-01T09:15:52.508Z] [INFO] [stdout]   - "Can you give me a specific example?" (example)
[2026-07-01T09:15:52.508Z] [INFO] [stdout] 
